                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260622-153-off763 t18260622-153-crimeloc765"></join>. On Tuesday, the 20th of June, I was going into the coal-vault, and saw the prisoner there. with a sack about two-thirds full of coals; he was stooping down, and trying to get it on his back; I came out, and locked him in - he was a stranger.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18260622-153-person894">
