            . I am footman to Mr. William Gambler. I found the prisoner in the vault, but the coals were not then in the sack.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I am a sweeper, and am forced to get dust; I had some dust in my bag, and saw some dustmen watching me; I ran down, and got into the coalvault.</p>
